<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Georg Gottsmann</head><p>Der Rat bittet Gottsmann, Hans III. von Wildenstein, Bürger zu Nürnberg, vor ihm und seinen Helfern zu sichern.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_126" id="62v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_126_r2l14">Görgen 
<del rend="strikethrough">VVıldenſteiner </del> Gocʒman </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_126_r2l15"><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> Gorg / vns hat fürgelegt Hans vvıldenſteiner <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> burger vvie </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_126_r2l16">daʒ er vor ew vnd <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> helffern vnſicher ſeẏ . / <expan>Bit<ex>en</ex></expan> . vvir ew daʒ Jr </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_126_r2l17">durch vnſern vvillen den <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Burger ſichern vvöllet auf </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_126_r2l18">freuntlich recht / vnd daʒ auch mit <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> helffern beſtellet / . daʒ <expan>wöll<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_126_r2l19">wir etc vnd het Jr dann cʒu dem <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> burger icht <expan>ʒuſprech<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_126_r2l20">darumb vvöllen wir ew <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>m</expan> ſcheinboten mit <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>m</expan> vollen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_126_r2l21">gewalt <expan>vnu<ex>er</ex>ʒogen</expan> ſlewnigs <expan>reht<ex>en</ex></expan> gerne helffen . vvenn wir des ermant </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_126_r2l22"><expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan> ſo <expan>derſ<ex>elb</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan> anheim iſt / vnd lat vns deʒ ewr <expan>freuntl<ex>ich</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_126_r2l23"><expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchrıb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> antvvurtt <expan>wid<ex>er</ex></expan> wiſʒen / beẏ diſem boten . / <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> vj poſt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_126_r2l24">vrbanj Anno . x<hi rend="sup">o</hi> . $ </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_126" id="62v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Görgen Goczman</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> Gorg, uns hat fürgelegt Hans Wildensteiner,
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> burger, wie daz er vor ew und
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> helffern unsicher sey.
                                <expan>Bit<ex>en</ex></expan> wir ew, daz ir durch unsern willen den
                                <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> burger sichern wöllet auf freuntlich recht
                        und daz auch mit <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> helffern bestellet, daz
                                <expan>wöll<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir etc. Und het ir dann czu dem
                                <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan> burger icht <expan>zu
                            sprech<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, darumb wöllen wir ew
                            <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex>m</expan> scheinboten mit <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>m</expan>
                        vollen gewalt <expan>unv<ex>er</ex>zogen</expan> slewnigs
                                <expan>reht<ex>en</ex></expan> gerne helffen, wenn wir des ermant
                                <expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan>, so <expan>ders<ex>elb</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan> anheim ist; und lat uns dez ewr
                                <expan>freuntl<ex>ich</ex></expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>schrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> antwurtt
                            <expan>wid<ex>er</ex></expan> wiszen bey disem boten.
                                <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> vi post Urbani anno x<hi rend="sup">o</hi>.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
